TT 2984 "Summer 1349. The Macula is evolving again in Hugo's blood, endangering his life and the lives of millions of others. The only way to save him may lie on an island Hugo regularly dreams about. After a perilous journey through Provence, they reach it and hear of a chapel that would be linked to the myth of the Macula." PROTO__ISLAND_FORTRESS_LOAD
